### 重力发生器

## 界面
gravity-generator-window-title = 重力发生器

## 界面字段名称
gravity-generator-window-status = 状态：
gravity-generator-window-power = 功率：
gravity-generator-window-eta = 预计时间：
gravity-generator-window-charge = 充能：

## 界面状态
gravity-generator-window-status-fully-charged = 充能完毕
gravity-generator-window-status-off = 关闭
gravity-generator-window-status-charging = 充能中
gravity-generator-window-status-discharging = 放电中

## 界面电源按钮
gravity-generator-window-power-on = 开启
gravity-generator-window-power-off = 关闭
gravity-generator-window-power-label = { $draw } / { $max } W

## 界面预计时间标签
gravity-generator-window-eta-none = 无
gravity-generator-window-eta-value = { TOSTRING($left, "m\\:ss") }

## 弹出提示
gravity-generator-unanchoring-failed = 无法解锚一台运行中的重力发生器。
